item.description:
This tutorial uses User and Organization Pages for general usage personal site
Create github pages repo Follow instructions from GitHub Pages, to create a user site repo (Remember to initialize it with a README.md file). Here we use my own repo foodtooth.github.io for simplicity.
Generate default jekyll site  Install Jekyll. Refer to jekyll installation doc git clone https://github.com/foodtooth/foodtooth.github.io jekyll new --force foodtooth.github.io cd foodtooth.github.io Follow instructions in Gemfile to enable gem &quot;github-pages&quot;
